<subSubSection id="5135F7BFD88D252169F1154768E52099" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="F3BA3E1CC0DB228E63AD14DF1B5F8284" pageId="0" pageNumber="407">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="576E8C524414AA0B90CD875E44D3A273" pageId="0" pageNumber="407">
Depicted in 
<bibRefCitation id="8B59D846E6A68D8065FB53373934116C" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1515/9783111625430-fm" author="Ahl, E" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum in Berlin" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" refId="B9" refString="Ahl, E, 1931b. Amphibia, Anura III, Polypedatidae. In: Hesse R (Ed.) Das Tierreich. Eine Zusammenstellung und Kennzeichnung der rezenten Tierformen. 55. Lieferung. Walter de Gruyter &amp; Co. Berlin und Leipzig, 477 pp. [+ (1-2)]. https://doi.org/10.1515/9783111625430-fm" title="Amphibia, Anura III, Polypedatidae. In: Hesse R (Ed.) Das Tierreich. Eine Zusammenstellung und Kennzeichnung der rezenten Tierformen. 55. Lieferung. Walter de Gruyter &amp; Co. Berlin und Leipzig, 477 pp. [+ (1 - 2)]." url="https://doi.org/10.1515/9783111625430-fm" year="1931 b">Ahl (1931b</bibRefCitation>
: 374, fig. 249). The type locality indicated by 
<bibRefCitation id="A8AA4BA25B63152A07F11CF50FB9BD97" author="Ahl, E" journalOrPublisher="Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum in Berlin" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" pagination="1 - 132" refId="B8" refString="Ahl, E, 1931a. Zur Systematik der afrikanischen Arten der Baumfroschgattung Hyperolius (Amph. Anur.). Mitteilungen aus dem Zoologischen Museum in Berlin 17 (1): 1 - 132" title="Zur Systematik der afrikanischen Arten der Baumfroschgattung Hyperolius (Amph. Anur.)." volume="17" year="1931 a">Ahl (1931a</bibRefCitation>
: 102) is misleading and composed of two different regions which are far apart. Houy was a member of the &quot;Lagone-Pama-Expedition 1912-13&quot;, which he accompanied as government doctor and zoologist to 
<normalizedToken id="A98520F3629DD93E3E4ECCB11017B4BA" originalValue="“Neu-Kamerun”">&quot;Neu-Kamerun&quot;</normalizedToken>
, and several natural history objects from this expedition were sent by him to ZMB. Together with the topographer and First Lieutenant Otto Tiller, he also accompanied the &quot;Expedition ins Zwischenseengebiet in Ostafrika&quot; [region between Lake Kivu and Lake Victoria] in 1911, the expedition directed by the colonial geographer Hans Heinrich Josef Meyer. According to the original label, the holotype of 
<taxonomicName id="8EF678992DB5407DA067554407026A8C" class="Amphibia" genus="H." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="H. houyi" order="Anura" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="houyi">
<emphasis id="52732AA38597466BE92C716FA9130BA0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="407">H. houyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was collected on 29 November 1911, at the end of 
<normalizedToken id="0F6E51C0F3A6624F8CE039E40F3D8493" originalValue="Meyer’s">Meyer's</normalizedToken>
expedition to East Afrika (see also 
<bibRefCitation id="DCE6B051920D183F43DF57B7C02BB8B2" author="Urban, I" journalOrPublisher="Petitpierre, Neuchatel" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" refId="B221" refString="Urban, I, 1917. Geschichte des Koeniglichen Botanischen Museums zu Berlin-Dahlem (1815-1913) nebst Aufzaehlung seiner Sammlungen. Beihefte zum Botanischen Centralblatt, 1. Abteilung: Anatomie, Histologie, Morphologie und Physiologie der Pflanzen 34(1/2): 1-457." title="Geschichte des Koeniglichen Botanischen Museums zu Berlin-Dahlem (1815 - 1913) nebst Aufzaehlung seiner Sammlungen. Beihefte zum Botanischen Centralblatt, 1. Abteilung: Anatomie, Histologie, Morphologie und Physiologie der Pflanzen 34 (1 / 2): 1 - 457." year="1917">Urban 1917</bibRefCitation>
). On the basis of the map showing the expedition route (
<bibRefCitation id="E3FD456087F06D3F1618B6247C934F08" author="Meyer, H" journalOrPublisher="Salamandra" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" refId="B134" refString="Meyer, H, 1913. Uebersichtskarte. Hans Meyer's Ostafrika-Expedition 1911. Mitteilungen aus den deutschen Schutzgebieten, Ergaenzungsheft 6." title="Uebersichtskarte. Hans Meyer's Ostafrika-Expedition 1911. Mitteilungen aus den deutschen Schutzgebieten, Ergaenzungsheft 6." year="1913">Meyer 1913</bibRefCitation>
), the corrected type locality for 
<taxonomicName id="9D9770B5B2258F7C720F9A14DB42EA14" class="Amphibia" genus="H." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="H. houyi" order="Anura" pageId="0" pageNumber="407" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="houyi">
<emphasis id="7F1B9AFBCA4E77AD44669E8304C5FDA5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="407">H. houyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has to be 
<normalizedToken id="3A47C882DDBF950E2A6A0783EB41CA14" originalValue="“SW-Ussagara”">&quot;SW-Ussagara&quot;</normalizedToken>
[southern Kilosa District, Morogoro Region, Tanzania].
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
